acism and apartheid.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Mrz 2024) 0aDemocracyzSouth Africa. 0aHuman rights workerszSouth AfricavBiography. 0aSocial movementszSouth Africa. 0aTeacherszSouth AfricavBiography. 4aArea Studies : African Studies. 4aEducation : Comparative Education. 4aEducation : Foundations of Education. 4aEducation : History of Education. 4aEducation : Social Context of Education. 4aGeneral Interest : Biography. 7aEDUCATION / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2014z978311149015140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978079147845540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791478455423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791478455/original  a978-3-11-149015-1  SUNY Press eBook Package 2014b2014  aGBV-deGruyter-alles